comments.body:
@kelynch Thank you for pulling these together. I have been looking at UI conventions for reporting harmful content outside of the Library world as well. I like the idea of a flag, as YouTube uses a FLAG icon with the label "Report". Facebook uses an EXCLAMATION IN A CHAT BUBBLE icon with "Report this post" as the label, which I think would also be appropriate. (Notice that YouTube also uses that icon, but with the label "Feedback".)

